Manage Group Benefits 
Group benefits are insurance plans offered to a group of people, such as employees and their dependents. Manage these insurance offerings in a rapidly evolving marketplace with Group Benefits on the Digital Insurance Platform.

Use a suite of integrated components and services to build end-to-end processes that improve Group Benefits quoting experiences, automate contract creation, and streamline enrollment.
Use Vlocity Insurance Group Benefits in the package data model to create quotes, manage plans and censuses, and enroll employees.
title: Managing Group Benefits on Salesforce
